<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2593632>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Distribution map for specimens of Chaeropus. Chaeropus ecaudatus ecaudatus in blue, C. e. occidentalis in green, C. yirratji sp. nov. in red, C. sp. indet. in black. Square = modern specimens; circles = subfossils (Holocene or younger in age); stars = Pleistocene fossils; triangles = oral history from Burbidge et al. (1988)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2593632/files/figure.png" ;
